150 discount\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will have to do a bit of work to get your money back, though.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"your money\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A cashback claim must be submitted within 30 days via the online claim form with the same information that the phone was bought with.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A cashback claim\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"30 days\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"the online claim form\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the same information\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"the phone\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The big pre-order deals are over, however.Samsung is not offering its free storage upgrade from 256GB to 512GB, nor is it still offering high trade-in prices for your old phone, or Samsung Care + for free.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The big pre-order deals\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"Samsung\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"its free storage\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"upgrade\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"256GB\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"512GB\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"high trade-in prices\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"your old phone\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"Samsung Care\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite this, \\u00a3150 off the headline price is still a solid deal andmatches the company's last Galaxy S24 sale earlier this month,which came just a few days before Galaxy Unpacked.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1184, \