ts again in the near future.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.998032847417544, \"rank\": 0.001971029893191883, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.998032847417544, \"rank\": 0.001971029893191883, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"double storage\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"other types\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"discounts\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"the near future\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company has repeatedly slashed the price its Galaxy S24 since it launched in January,as has Google with its Pixel 8.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9995527012657401, \"rank\": 0.0004474983083628092, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The company\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"its Galaxy S24\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"its Pixel\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both companies have been locked in a price war for the last seven months and with Google's upcoming Pixel 9 launch, followed by Apple's iPhone 16